<P>
   (Main Display and Lead Story)
</P>
<P>
   TV-REPLAY (Undated) _ A new, innocuous-looking consumer
electronic device known as a personal video recorder (PVR) is not
much different in nature from the video cassette recorder, and very
few of them have been sold to date. And yet an increasing number of
executives at television networks and advertising agencies have
their ears nervously on alert. By Bill Carter.
</P>
