<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-04 17:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9012 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-`SOS'-COMPUTER-BIZ-65     07-04 1809
