<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-04 22:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9214 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SAFIRE-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      07-04 0740
