   (NYT1) LOS ANGELES -- July 4, 1999 -- FIBER-CHANNEL-TECH, 7-4 --
H.K. Desai, foreground, president and chief executive of Qlogic,
and Paul F. Folino, president and chief executive of Emulex, at the
companies' headquarters. The two companies are vying for leadership
in fiber channel technology, a new industry-standard approach to
high-speed data transfer between computers and separate
data-storage disk drives. (Ed Carreon/New York Times Photo)
</P>
